      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For a truly high-level, globally respected look, the standard is classic, understated elegance—think tailored, well-fitting garments in neutral colors. Men should stick to dark suits, crisp shirts, and polished shoes, while women should opt for sophisticated suiting or elegant dresses that are modest and impeccably tailored. Grooming must be meticulous; hair should be neat, nails clean, and makeup, if worn, should be subtle and professional, avoiding anything flashy or distracting.",
